text: Love the cai fan stall opened by a young man  at this kopitiam, he had very good attitude and the dishes are very high quality. The servings he gave was generous. Rice quality also is great! Will be a regular just for his food!

My frequent breakfast spot. Good place to meet friends in the AMK area. Not too crowded, big carpark, walking distance from Lentor MRT. Prata, Dosai, nasi lemak, bak chor mee, roast meat... all pretty good,. Korean stall too.
Nice quiet place for a drink.
